Rushydro to Invest 21 Bln Rubles in Innovations, Vedomosti Says

-- B y   M a r i n a   S y s o y e v a
-- 
2011-08-25T04:21:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-25/rushydro-to-invest-21-bln-rubles-in-innovations-vedomosti-says.html
OAO Rushydro plans to invest 21
billion rubles ($725 million) in innovations to cut production
costs and increase energy efficiency,  Vedomosti  reported, citing
a company document.  The investments will help to increase energy output by 4
percent and bring the share of renewable sources in that output
to 5 percent in 10 years, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marina Sysoyeva in Moscow 
 msysoyeva@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
